title: Poverty Map Bolivia Lvl 2
name: Poverty Map Bolivia Lvl 2
description:
Shows the Poverty Headcount Index for 2001, which shows the porportion of the population whose welfare falls below a poverty line, in this case Bolivia's national poverty line.
In 2001 63% percent of the population in Boliva lived below the poverty line.
Source: Center for International Earth Science Information Network (CIESIN). "Bolivia Headcount Index, 2001." Global Distribution of Poverty. 2007. http://www.ciesin.columbia.edu/povmap.
